<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Tools | Hallo89</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="menu.css">
    <script src="global.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="info_mode">
    {% import 'templates/glb_box.njk' as box %}
    <div id="containers">

      {% call box.box('3D Magic', '3DMagic') %}
        A tool which displays minecraft models from their JSON format in a model viewing environment, featuring an integrated text editor to modify the model
      {% endcall %}

      {% call box.box('Random figure generator', 'RFG') %}
        A tool to generate random numbers. Their amount, starting and ending point and the length of one figure after its comma is customizable
      {% endcall %}

      {% call box.box('Mocking generator', 'mocking') %}
        A tool to generate text iN ThE MOcKboB sTylE which is no outdated meme at all
      {% endcall %}

      {% call box.box('Spacing generator', 'spacing') %}
        A tool converting text to a format alternating between characters and spaces. The amount of spaces in between every character is customizable
      {% endcall %}

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
